    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It has been such a reliable ride for me and honestly still looks fantastic cruising down the street! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014definitely well-loved and well-taken care of, so it's totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable daily driver that still feels fresh and fun, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
