    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. This example delivers 333 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and a valve clearance adjustment was recently performed to ensure the valvetrain operates within spec. With its high-revving atmospheric induction and balanced 50/50 weight distribution, this E46 provides a pure, analog driving experience that modern sports cars cannot replicate.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
