    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle offers a fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained, reliable driver that presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with a clean, fresh scent. The leather seating surfaces remain supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's side bolster. All technology features, including the infotainment system, climate control, and power accessories, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has been serviced regularly, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive over bumps. It is a solid, honest car that has been cared for properly and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
