      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable daily driver, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic, well-loved car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Would love for it to go to a good home\u2014come check it out!",
      "price": 32500.0,
