    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is primed for the enthusiast, with the 'Big Three' already addressed: the rear subframe has been reinforced, the VANOS system overhauled with upgraded seals, and rod bearings replaced for long-term reliability. The drivetrain remains stout, utilizing the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential to manage power delivery. Suspension is enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis maintains its legendary handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical integrity is prioritized, including a recent valve clearance adjustment and cooling system refresh. A driver-focused machine with excellent tactile feedback and linear power delivery.",
